utton\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 14, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bbq1665702713800.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bbq1665702713800.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bbq1665702713800.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bbq1665702713800\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">Delete a Project or Reference\n    Object</h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Deleting a project does not delete the objects it contains. It only deleted the\n    references to those objects.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbq1665702713800__li_d1442e1_d1443e1_d1444e1\">To delete an object in a project, select it in the Project Structure Editor, right-click and choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Delete</span>.\n <p class=\"p\" id=\"bbq1665702713800__p_d3926e1_d3927e1_d3928e1\">Deleting a reference object does not delete the object it refers to. It remains in the Repository, where you can find and open it using the U-Bar.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbq1665702713800__li_d1445e1_d1446e1_d1447e1\">To delete an entire project, open it and choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Actions &gt;Delete</span></span>.\n <p class=\"p\" id=\"bbq1665702713800__p_d3929e1_d3930e1_d3931e1\">You are asked to confirm that the Project should be deleted.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/spu1692183913093.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Projects</a><p>A project is a collection of references to main development objects. It is used to create and organize components, modeled entities, and libraries that are needed to build the application.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ygt1665702713729.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Project Editor</a><p>The Project Editor is automatically opened when you create or open a project in the Uniface IDE. It is used to create and organize main development objects, and export the project and its objects. Objects can belong to more than one project.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525961\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525961\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Delete a Project or Reference Object Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 14, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Delete a Project or Reference Object Deleting a project does not delete the objects it contains. It only deleted the references to those objects. To delete an object in a project, select it in the Project Structure Editor, right-click and choose Delete . Deleting a reference object does not delete the object it refers to. It remains in the Repository, where you can find and open it using the U-Bar. To delete an entire project, open it and choose Actions >Delete . You are asked to confirm that the Project should be deleted. Related Links Projects A project is a collection of references to main development objects. It is used to create and organize components, modeled entities, and libraries that are needed to build the application. Project Editor The Project Editor is automatically opened when you create or open a project in the Uniface IDE. It is used to create and organize main development objects, and export the project and its objects. Objects can belong to more than one project. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}